&lt;/div>
&lt;h2>Verification — what the reviewer looks for&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="verification--what-the-reviewer-looks-for">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#verification--what-the-reviewer-looks-for" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Deployment now references &lt;code>3.4.1+&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Verification checklist is concrete and executable.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>PR body documents any observed tenant-boundary anomalies and next actions.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
